## ProtonVersion → wineVersion Identifier Mapping

```kotlin
private fun protonVersionToPattern(version: ProtonVersion): String? = when (version) {
    ProtonVersion.PROTON_10_0   -> "10.0"
    ProtonVersion.PROTON_9_0    -> "9.0"
    ProtonVersion.PROTON_8_0    -> "8.0"
    ProtonVersion.PROTON_7_0    -> "7.0"
    ProtonVersion.WINE_GE_LATEST,
    ProtonVersion.STOCK_WINE    -> null   // no version enforcement for these
}
```

The installed version is found by matching `profile.verName.contains(pattern)` on the
`ContentsManager` proton profiles. Container wineVersion is `"proton-" + profile.verName`
(lowercase, no verCode suffix — e.g. `"proton-9.0-arm64ec"`).

