## KnownGameFixes — What You Must Set per Entry

Every `GameFix` entry should declare ALL of the following where applicable:

| Field | What it controls | Auto-enforced? |
|---|---|---|
| `protonVersion` | container.wineVersion at launch | ✅ Yes — ContainerUtils |
| `dxVersion` | DXVK vs VKD3D wrapper | ✅ Yes — recommender + applyGameConfig |
| `extraEnvVars` | WINEDLLOVERRIDES, DXVK_ASYNC, etc. | ✅ Yes — always last in applyGameConfig |
| `launchArgs` | GN_WINE_LAUNCH_ARGS | ✅ Yes — always last in applyGameConfig |
| `forceUseLegacyDrm` | bypasses ColdClientLoader | ✅ Yes — LaunchOrchestrator |
| `gameExePath` | override launched .exe | ✅ Yes — XServerScreen |
| `requiresD8VK` | d8vk (OpenGL DXVK backend) | ✅ Yes — recommender |
| `reason` | explains why — required for future maintenance | ❌ No (string comment) |

**Never leave `reason` empty.** Future contributors must understand why a fix exists.

